lanning.\r\n\r\n---\r\nThe werewolves of Millers Hollow\r\n\r\nA game for at least 8 and up to 20 players (or more)\r\n\r\nThe villagers of Millers Hollow are dealing with a menace\r\nMore and more are getting killed by deadly werewolfes every night. They know that the wolves are among them but nobody knows who it is.\r\nAn interesting and socialising game about intrigue lies and influence.\r\nWho's trustworthy and who not?"",""ConferenceDayId"":""8af3e817-2b00-11e6-af7b-066e23d209cf"",""StartTime"":""20:00:00"",""EndTime"":""00:00:00"",""Duration"":""04:00:00"",""ConferenceRoomId"":""83527dfe-cf2d-467f-b24c-0aa595049263"",""PanelHosts"":""Carijet"",""IsDeviatingFromConBook"":""0""},{""Id"":""c0e8e8af-6fa6-4422-abdc-d2f7abe37ea2"",""LastChangeDateTimeUtc"":""2016-07-15T11:40:02Z"",""IsDeleted"":""0"",""SourceEventId"":""938"",""ImageId"":null,""Slug"":""art_show_thur"",""Title"":""Art Show"",""SubTitle"":"""",""ConferenceTrackId"":""8af3638e-2b00-11e6-af7b-066e23d209cf"",""Abstract"":""This year's Art Show again presents a multitude of international artists. See your favorites, bid on whatever you like, and buy art for your home!"",""Description"":""This year's Art Show again presents a multitude of international artists. See your favorites, bid on whatever you like, and buy art for your home!\r\n\r\nA separate registration is needed for bidding to get bid stickers.\r\n\r\nYou will have a final chance at bidding in the Art Show closing. Here it will be determined who will make the final offer on a piece of art - or whether, perhaps, a contested piece goes to auction. \r\nImportant: The closing is a fast and decisive event. You need to have bid stickers at hand to participate, so we can avoid crowding the show area with spectators. Bid stickers will only be available until 30 minutes before the closing. During the closing, we will not hand out new stickers, so make sure you have enough to place your final bids.\r\n\r\nIn the voice auction, you will have to defend your selection against other prospective buyers. Please note that this year's auction starts earlier than in previous years.\r\n\r\nBids must be placed in Euros, and paid cash on site.\r\n\r\nLook out for more information at the Art Show and read the bulletin boards for last-minute details!"",""ConferenceDayId"":""8af3def1-2b00-11e6-af7b-066e23d209cf"",""StartTime"":""12:00:00"",""EndTime"":""20:00:00"",""Duration"":""08:00:00"",""ConferenceRoomId"":""27400e29-a1d2-4598-a993-ad25addc69eb"",""PanelHosts"":""Cairyn, Blue_Panther"",""IsDeviatingFromConBook"":""0""},{""Id"":""c184e483-c1a1-4bd2-bfdf-fbfcd42f22c8"",""LastChangeDateTimeUtc"":""2016-07-07T23:40:01Z"",""IsDeleted"":""0"",""SourceEventId"":""1065"",""ImageId"":null,""Slug"":""charity_retro_games_tournament_3"",""Title"":""Charity Retro Games Tournament "",""SubTitle"":""Slot 3"",""ConferenceTrackId"":""188bede5-032a-46f9-bae1-6f6fda3cafef"",""Abstract"":""Whether you\u2019re young enough to find 80s computer games cool and quirky, or old enough to find them nice and nostalgic, this is your chance to play some classic games and win some seriously nice prizes! Enter the tournaments for a small fee and see how you stack up! All money goes directly to help our charity."",""Description"":""Whether you\u2019re young enough to find 80s computer games cool and quirky, or old enough to find them nice and nostalgic, this is your chance to play some classic games and win some seriously nice prizes! Enter the tournaments for a small fee and see how you stack up! All money goes directly to help our charity."",""ConferenceDayId"":""8af3f161-2b00-11e6-af7b-066e23d209cf"",""StartTime"":""15:30:00"",""EndTime"":""17:00:00"",""Duration"":""01:30:00"",""ConferenceRoomId"":""cda5a2b5-cc50-4710-aa92-7cae54f1edcc"",""PanelHosts"":""Dibs Razell, Pinky"",""IsDeviatingFromConBook"":""0""},{""Id"":""c68a209d-c517-4367-8886-8710075a2286"",""LastChangeDateTimeUtc"":""2016-07-15T17:40:02Z"",""IsDeleted"":""0"",""SourceEventId"":""967"",""I